com.google.android.apps.muzei.api
Class Artwork

java.lang.Object
  com.google.android.apps.muzei.api.Artwork
public class Artwork
extends Object

A serializable object representing a single artwork produced by a MuzeiArtSource. An artwork is simple an image along with some metadata.

To create an instance, use the Artwork.Builder class.
